      "span_text": "SW480 cells were seeded at a concentration of 2x10  per well (6-well, Coring) and the next morning they were transiently transfected with pGsh644, pGsh1451, pGsh1938, pGsh2231, pG4 and HK vectors with Lipofectamine 2000 (Invitrogen, Jefferson City, MO, USA) according to the manufacturer's instructions."
